# Exclude
Exclude	exclude	/opt/accomplist/my-routedns.exclude!	/opt/accomplist/work/exclude.list	7200	@DOMAIN	@IP

# Whitelist Domains
WhiteList	white!	/opt/accomplist/whitelist/plain.white.domain.list!	/opt/accomplist/work/white.list	7200	@DOMAIN	@IP
AllowList	white	https://raw.githubusercontent.com/cbuijs/my-allowlist/master/allow.list	/opt/accomplist/work/allow.list	7200	@DOMAIN	@IP
NextDNS-Recommended-White	white!	/opt/accomplist/nextdns-recommended/plain.white.domain.list!	/opt/accomplist/work/nextdns-recommended-white.list	7200	@DOMAIN	@IP
NextDNS-Affiliate-White	white	https://github.com/nextdns/metadata/blob/master/privacy/affiliate-tracking-domains	/opt/accomplist/work/nextdns-affiliate-white.list	7200	@DOMAIN	@IP
Router-WL	white	https://raw.githubusercontent.com/cbuijs/my-allowlist/master/allow.list	/opt/accomplist/work/router-wl.list	7200	@DOMAIN	@IP

